1.title: Malibu Castle & Drinks with Mr. Wonderful

episode of.title: Secret Lives of the Super Rich (TV Series 2013– )

1.plot: The most expensive mansion in Malibu; "Shark Tank" investor Kevin O'Leary's $65K whisky order; a real-estate tycoon driving his car right into a bay; an adrenaline junkie's $120K price tag to climb Mount Everest.

2.title: Kim K's Gold-Eating Bestie & Ferrari Donuts

episode of.title: Secret Lives of the Super Rich (TV Series 2013– )

2.plot: Meet Kim Kardashian's gold-eating bestie: Foodgod. Find out why the most over-the-top mega-mansion in New Jersey has been sitting empty for nearly a decade. Burn rubber in a rare $350K Ferrari. Take a zipline ride to a $31 million winter wonderland. Get a rare look inside the remote desert palace of a Gucci heiress.

3.title: Surf's Up Mansion & A $200 Bottle of Beer

episode of.title: Secret Lives of the Super Rich (TV Series 2013– )

3.plot: Meet the super-rich surfer who has the coolest bachelor pad in SoCal. See a Wall Street bigwig have his private jet transformed into a flying office. The billionaire beer lover who created the most expensive brew in America. Moon rocks turned into cufflinks that cost more than a car. Take the wheel of a racecar legend's $3 million Ferrari.

4.title: Rock Star Living & $30 Million Superyacht

episode of.title: Secret Lives of the Super Rich (TV Series 2013– )

4.plot: Inside the Hollywood mansion designed by rock 'n' roll legend Lenny Kravitz; on board a $30 million superyacht; a helicopter trip to a heart-shaped private island; a mega-home on Aspen's "Billionaires' Row"; a jeweler known as "Diamond Joe"; the priciest cheesesteak in Philadelphia.

5.title: Oil Tycoon's $250M Ranch & Looking for Love

episode of.title: Secret Lives of the Super Rich (TV Series 2013– )

5.plot: A tour of billionaire financier Boone Pickens' Texas-sized ranch; a wealthy millennial goes luxury watch shopping; the secret lounge for Lamborghini-loving VIPs; a millionaire goes on a date in Beverly Hills, California.

6.title: Ultimate Coffee House & Lambos on Ice

episode of.title: Secret Lives of the Super Rich (TV Series 2013– )

6.plot: Cuban coffee baron's Miami estate; an icy playground for Lamborghini lovers; feng shui expert to the super-rich; $72 million Hamptons summer home; the world's most expensive store.

imdb.plot outline: Secret Lives of the Super Rich is an American television series, hosted by Robert Frank (X)', airing on CNBC. The series explores how wealthy people live, what they buy and how they travel. It regularly features mansions, luxury cars and aircraft and expensive jewelry.
